{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/critical_hit.png?t=1733763436\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/critical_attack.gif?t=1733763436\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take up arms against the Beasts with impactful and gratifying back-and-forth combat. Use the Guardians' diverse abilities and skills to land exciting <strong>Critical Hits</strong>, causing the party to enter the <strong>Inspired</strong> state for 3 turns where they are faster, deal more damage, and are resilient to negative statuses. You'll know you've landed a <strong>Critical Hit</strong> when a character cuts in, and the music ramps up in volume and intensity!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An <strong>Evolution</strong> of <strong>Critical Hits</strong> in <strong>Turn-Based Combat</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique character <strong>Skills</strong> and <strong>Guardian Abilities</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Class Progression</strong> and unlocking <strong>New Classes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Music</strong> in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dungeon Exploration</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/delve.png?t=1733763436\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/explore.gif?t=1733763436\" />Experience the stories of a people born in perpetual servitude towards one goal: <i>defeating the Beasts.</i> For as long as we can remember, the Beasts have risen from the mountains, and for as long as we can remember, we have deigned to destroy them. With a seemingly never-ending struggle, <i>what can keep you going?</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">World and Narrative</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>Modern</strong> take on RPG storytelling from a <strong>Small Indie Developer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carefully crafted and <strong>Detailed Lore</strong> in a <strong>Unique Fantasy</strong> setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An <strong>Appropriately</strong> sized world and <strong>Concise</strong> JRPG story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evolving NPC Stories</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/dani_fey.png?t=1733763436\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/extras/dani_intro.gif?t=1733763436\" />Experience the story through the eyes of newly graduated Guardian Dani Fey, along with her friends and comrades. Oftentimes too brash and sarcastic for her own good, Dani will need to balance the grueling and monotonous duties of being a Guardian while struggling to retain her sense of self.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Characters and Art</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anime</strong> styled character art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crisp <strong>Pixel</strong> art sprites with <strong>Realistically Rendered</strong> environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>Comprehensive</strong> and <strong>Distinguished</strong> soundtrack</p></li></ul></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2603350?t=1733763436","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1733763436","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603350/f3